WEBVTT

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.920
Why do I keep hallucinating?

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:23.159
Must be exhausted.

00:01:23.159 --> 00:01:25.079
What to do, what to do?

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:35.560
It's real.

00:01:35.920 --> 00:01:36.680
It's real.

00:01:39.879 --> 00:01:40.719
I'm dead tired.

00:01:40.920 --> 00:01:41.840
Tired.

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:43.840
I brought you something delicious.

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:45.599
What?

00:01:45.719 --> 00:01:47.079
Scrambled eggs with tomatoes.

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:47.840
Let me see.

00:01:51.799 --> 00:01:52.560
Look.

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:54.400
You made this?

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:56.280
You're so good.

00:01:58.879 --> 00:02:00.359
Isn't this from that time...

00:02:01.079 --> 00:02:02.040
It's all been investigated.

00:02:02.959 --> 00:02:04.640
The Long Group sent people to sneak photos.

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:05.799
The Long Group.

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:07.439
Do you remember before,

00:02:07.439 --> 00:02:09.439
when my domain site was hacked?

00:02:09.960 --> 00:02:11.639
That was also Long Technologies' doing.

00:02:12.159 --> 00:02:12.960
Look here.

00:02:13.759 --> 00:02:14.280
This...

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:15.960
This row.

00:02:16.319 --> 00:02:18.080
The Long Group isn't just targeting me.

00:02:19.159 --> 00:02:20.599
They are like a malignant tumor.

00:02:20.879 --> 00:02:22.319
Causing harm wherever they go.

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:24.080
Back in the Computer City days,

00:02:24.319 --> 00:02:25.840
they started by swindling and cheating.

00:02:26.439 --> 00:02:29.280
Then forced acquisition and demolition in real estate.

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:32.280
Then loan sharking to suck people dry.

00:02:34.599 --> 00:02:36.919
Now they want to whitewash themselves as a tech company.

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:39.479
But the evil in their bones can't be changed.

00:02:41.199 --> 00:02:41.759
Ruochu.

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:44.680
Many things have changed this time around.

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:48.479
Like the smuggling case where you were hit by a car last time.

00:02:49.159 --> 00:02:50.000
It was exposed early.

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:51.000
They didn't succeed.

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:53.080
But now they want to use Zhou Honghai.

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:55.199
Using Long Technologies in the open

00:02:55.199 --> 00:02:56.680
to attack Extraordinary Tech.

00:02:57.039 --> 00:02:58.199
But in the dark,

00:02:58.759 --> 00:03:01.080
they'll surely use dirty tricks against us again.

00:03:02.759 --> 00:03:03.639
Before, I...

00:03:03.800 --> 00:03:04.759
...thought that Brother Honghai

00:03:04.759 --> 00:03:06.240
was just being used by the Long Group.

00:03:06.639 --> 00:03:07.479
Now it seems

00:03:07.879 --> 00:03:09.599
he joined the Long Group voluntarily.

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:17.520
Ruochu.

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:20.000
You must be extra careful from today on.

00:03:20.240 --> 00:03:21.680
Never go out alone.

00:03:21.680 --> 00:03:23.080
Don't answer calls from strangers.

00:03:23.080 --> 00:03:25.199
I'll come keep you company whenever I can.

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:27.199
I've also upgraded the apartment's surveillance.

00:03:29.360 --> 00:03:30.240
No matter what happens,

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:31.599
I will protect you.

00:03:32.159 --> 00:03:33.680
I won't let you face any accidents again.

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:37.039
I will protect you too.

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:37.759
Chen Fan.

00:03:39.039 --> 00:03:41.639
This life isn't just about you alone.

00:03:42.240 --> 00:03:43.560
We'll shoulder any difficulties together.

00:03:43.759 --> 00:03:44.479
Okay?

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:47.080
Don't push me away anymore.

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:15.039
Slow down.

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:16.079
All right, Mr. Zhou.

00:04:22.399 --> 00:04:22.959
Manager Zhou.

00:04:24.079 --> 00:04:24.480
Mr. Liu.

00:04:24.480 --> 00:04:26.079
The route you designed is excellent.

00:04:26.399 --> 00:04:27.959
It avoided several police checkpoints.

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:30.079
Once this batch of cargo arrives safely at the port,

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:31.240
the Southeast Asia route

00:04:31.560 --> 00:04:32.279
will also be handed over to you.

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:33.279
Really?

00:04:40.199 --> 00:04:41.759
I thought you handled Extraordinary Tech.

00:04:42.279 --> 00:04:43.839
I didn't expect more trouble to pop up.

00:04:43.839 --> 00:04:45.680
Where did this Extraordinary Cleaner come from?

00:04:46.040 --> 00:04:47.000
Extraordinary Cleaner.

00:04:49.480 --> 00:04:51.079
Our plugin had just been rolled out,

00:04:51.079 --> 00:04:52.600
when Extraordinary Tech immediately released

00:04:52.600 --> 00:04:54.199
the Extraordinary Cleaner antivirus software.

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:56.480
It pops up a warning if it detects Dragon Wing,

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:57.959
and even includes a one-click removal function.

00:04:58.360 --> 00:04:59.160
Now look at this mess.

00:04:59.600 --> 00:05:01.240
User uninstall rates have soared to 70%.

00:05:01.560 --> 00:05:02.560
Damn you, Chen Fan.

00:05:02.839 --> 00:05:03.959
You just have to oppose me.

00:05:03.959 --> 00:05:05.399
You just can't stand seeing me succeed, can you?

00:05:05.399 --> 00:05:06.680
Even the click rates for ads

00:05:06.680 --> 00:05:08.199
bundled with Dragon Wing have dropped.

00:05:08.279 --> 00:05:09.800
The installers are rushing us for a replacement plan.

00:05:09.800 --> 00:05:10.480
Useless!

00:05:10.920 --> 00:05:12.680
Didn't I tell you to add anti-blocking code?

00:05:12.680 --> 00:05:14.279
We tried, but it didn't work.

00:05:16.879 --> 00:05:18.399
Then put a shell around the plugin.

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:20.079
Make a fake system pop-up

00:05:20.199 --> 00:05:22.040
to trick users into closing Extraordinary Cleaner.

00:05:22.040 --> 00:05:24.279
Then find a way to locate those installation software vendors.

00:05:24.439 --> 00:05:25.279
Offer them kickbacks.

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:26.800
Have them use the boot screen

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:27.600
to force a silent installation.

00:05:27.600 --> 00:05:29.120
But the cyber police in three provinces

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:29.759
have already summoned us.

00:05:29.759 --> 00:05:30.680
Then you come sit in my seat!

00:05:31.959 --> 00:05:32.800
Do as I say!

00:05:42.040 --> 00:05:42.959
Chen Fan.

00:05:43.399 --> 00:05:46.040
I will fight you to the bitter end in this life.

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:51.199
Beautiful work, brother.

00:05:51.319 --> 00:05:52.040
It had to be you.

00:05:52.279 --> 00:05:53.439
Our Extraordinary Cleaner

00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:54.759
has smashed their Dragon Wing plugin

00:05:54.759 --> 00:05:55.879
to smithereens.

00:05:57.399 --> 00:05:57.959
Wait.

00:05:58.279 --> 00:05:58.959
Look at this.

00:06:04.040 --> 00:06:05.319
The icons of these two plugins

00:06:05.319 --> 00:06:06.800
are almost exactly the same.

00:06:07.199 --> 00:06:09.279
The interface and button layout are the same too.

00:06:09.959 --> 00:06:10.319
Brother,

00:06:10.759 --> 00:06:12.319
they definitely copied us.

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:13.759
I don't know either.

00:06:14.120 --> 00:06:14.879
I've never seen it.

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:18.319
Chen Fan

00:06:18.839 --> 00:06:19.399
Look,

00:06:19.839 --> 00:06:20.680
our Extraordinary Cleaner

00:06:20.680 --> 00:06:22.240
was copied as soon as it launched.

00:06:22.240 --> 00:06:23.920
I suspect it's the Long Group again.

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:24.959
It's definitely them.

00:06:26.240 --> 00:06:27.160
Not only did they copy it,

00:06:27.160 --> 00:06:28.800
but they also registered the patent first.

00:06:28.800 --> 00:06:29.839
And now they're biting back,

00:06:29.839 --> 00:06:32.040
claiming we copied their core algorithm

00:06:32.040 --> 00:06:33.279
and demanding compensation.

00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:35.480
This is the court summons that arrived this morning.

00:06:36.079 --> 00:06:36.560
No way.

00:06:37.279 --> 00:06:38.519
He actually dares to sue us?

00:06:38.879 --> 00:06:39.959
That's some nerve.

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:41.079
Evil cannot prevail over good.

00:06:41.480 --> 00:06:42.519
If they dare to sue,

00:06:43.079 --> 00:06:44.560
we dare to respond.

00:06:45.199 --> 00:06:47.720
Manager Zhou, you did a beautiful job with this Super Cleaner.

00:06:47.720 --> 00:06:49.160
The installation rate keeps rising.

00:06:49.160 --> 00:06:50.879
The retention rate for the Dragon Wing plugin

00:06:51.079 --> 00:06:51.959
has rebounded significantly.

00:06:51.959 --> 00:06:52.759
You flatter me.

00:06:52.759 --> 00:06:53.680
Tell me,

00:06:54.079 --> 00:06:55.279
how did you overtake them?

00:06:55.959 --> 00:06:57.120
Their Extraordinary Cleaner

00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:58.480
actually used Liang Shichu's

00:06:58.480 --> 00:07:00.199
earliest antivirus software as a base for optimization.

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:02.040
Liang Shichu often asked for my opinion back then,

00:07:02.040 --> 00:07:03.839
so I've always known that core logic.

00:07:04.079 --> 00:07:06.800
I gave them a taste of their own medicine.

00:07:08.240 --> 00:07:10.199
I had my men rewrite the code using VD,

00:07:10.199 --> 00:07:12.040
and swapped in a similar icon and interface.

00:07:12.040 --> 00:07:13.800
They can't tell which is which at all.

00:07:13.800 --> 00:07:15.839
I knew bringing you on board would be useful.

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:17.800
A small reward.

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:18.639
Keep up the good work.

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:20.560
The company won't treat you unfairly.

00:07:21.800 --> 00:07:22.600
President Liu,

00:07:23.279 --> 00:07:24.600
I will give it my all.

00:07:24.959 --> 00:07:27.079
You clearly developed this software first.

00:07:27.079 --> 00:07:28.560
Didn't you apply for a patent back then?

00:07:28.560 --> 00:07:30.279
I was busy fighting tech wars with them every day,

00:07:30.279 --> 00:07:31.439
and I had to deal with school,

00:07:31.439 --> 00:07:33.399
plus manage the internet cafe and the club.

00:07:33.560 --> 00:07:34.879
I was so busy I completely forgot.

00:07:35.040 --> 00:07:36.560
If we apply right now,

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:37.360
is there still time?

00:07:37.360 --> 00:07:38.279
It's too late.

00:07:38.800 --> 00:07:40.600
The patent office only recognizes the filing date,

00:07:40.600 --> 00:07:42.040
not who created it first.

00:07:42.680 --> 00:07:43.639
Then what should we do?

00:07:44.600 --> 00:07:45.040
Don't panic.

00:07:45.360 --> 00:07:46.680
I've handled a similar case before.

00:07:47.079 --> 00:07:48.959
We can countersue them

00:07:49.160 --> 00:07:50.959
for patent invalidation and trade secret infringement.

00:07:51.759 --> 00:07:52.680
When have you ever done that?

00:07:53.399 --> 00:07:54.000
Listen to her.

00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:55.040
Brother Liang,

00:07:55.399 --> 00:07:56.959
go find the evidence from when

00:07:56.959 --> 00:07:58.639
you were developing this software.

00:07:59.040 --> 00:07:59.920
Code manuscripts,

00:07:59.920 --> 00:08:00.759
handwritten logs,

00:08:00.759 --> 00:08:01.279
interface sketches,

00:08:01.279 --> 00:08:02.560
anything like that will work.

00:08:02.759 --> 00:08:03.680
It's best if you can prove

00:08:03.680 --> 00:08:05.240
that the core parts of this software

00:08:05.240 --> 00:08:06.439
were all completed by you.

00:08:06.879 --> 00:08:07.319
Okay.

00:08:07.319 --> 00:08:07.720
Also,

00:08:07.879 --> 00:08:10.160
go dig into their software code.

00:08:10.279 --> 00:08:11.560
It would be best if we can show by comparison

00:08:11.680 --> 00:08:13.240
that theirs is just a simple reorganization

00:08:13.240 --> 00:08:14.240
and routine technical patch.

00:08:14.279 --> 00:08:15.079
I'll have them start digging right away.

00:08:15.879 --> 00:08:16.600
By the way, Brother Liang,

00:08:17.199 --> 00:08:18.920
in the initial version's

00:08:18.920 --> 00:08:19.639
underlying code,

00:08:19.639 --> 00:08:20.879
did you bury any special markers?

00:08:20.879 --> 00:08:22.519
Right, this is also very important.

00:08:22.519 --> 00:08:22.879
Markers?

00:08:23.079 --> 00:08:24.079
It's best if there's a witness.

00:08:24.279 --> 00:08:25.279
Is there anyone who can prove

00:08:25.279 --> 00:08:26.480
your development process back then?

00:08:27.600 --> 00:08:28.439
Wenjie.

00:08:29.079 --> 00:08:30.439
But he's still serving his sentence.

00:08:30.839 --> 00:08:31.680
It doesn't matter.

00:08:31.839 --> 00:08:33.320
Inmates can also testify.

00:08:33.840 --> 00:08:34.879
Even if he can't be there in person,

00:08:34.879 --> 00:08:36.159
video or written testimony

00:08:36.159 --> 00:08:36.960
will work.

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:38.440
Gosh, Ruochu.

00:08:38.960 --> 00:08:40.559
You sound like a professional lawyer.

00:08:41.679 --> 00:08:42.679
Gosh, Ruochu.

00:08:42.679 --> 00:08:45.039
You sound like a professional lawyer.

00:09:08.600 --> 00:09:09.399
Hello.

00:09:09.639 --> 00:09:11.759
I'd like to apply for an inmate to testify in court.

00:09:18.879 --> 00:09:20.440
Wenjie, thanks to you this time...

00:09:25.679 --> 00:09:27.600
The court has accepted your written testimony.

00:09:27.600 --> 00:09:28.879
And the code comparison records.

00:09:29.279 --> 00:09:30.399
We won the lawsuit.

00:09:32.039 --> 00:09:32.799
And...

00:09:33.320 --> 00:09:35.559
The court also ruled the Long Group's patent invalid.

00:09:36.240 --> 00:09:37.879
They ruled it was malicious litigation.

00:09:38.240 --> 00:09:39.480
You really helped us out a lot.

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:43.000
Actually...

00:09:43.799 --> 00:09:44.759
I didn't really do anything.

00:09:44.759 --> 00:09:46.519
Long Technologies has already kicked Zhou Honghai out.

00:09:50.759 --> 00:09:51.639
Really?

00:09:53.000 --> 00:09:53.679
That's great.

00:09:53.679 --> 00:09:55.480
So, regarding the things you did before...

00:09:55.840 --> 00:09:56.879
Did he put you up to it?

00:09:57.279 --> 00:09:58.039
If you speak up now...

00:09:58.039 --> 00:09:59.120
No one can protect him anymore.

00:10:07.120 --> 00:10:08.600
It was my own greed.

00:10:08.759 --> 00:10:09.679
You aren't that kind of person.

00:10:11.639 --> 00:10:13.279
The internet cafe and club operations...

00:10:13.279 --> 00:10:14.080
Were all in your hands.

00:10:14.679 --> 00:10:15.720
If you were greedy, you would've acted long ago.

00:10:15.720 --> 00:10:16.240
Brother Fan.

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:18.879
Stop talking about it.

00:10:21.440 --> 00:10:23.000
I'll be out in two years.

00:10:23.639 --> 00:10:24.799
Please stop asking, okay?

00:10:26.279 --> 00:10:27.559
You still have a younger sister.

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:36.799
Brother Fan.

00:10:38.000 --> 00:10:39.279
Can you do me a favor?

00:10:39.600 --> 00:10:41.000
In our internet cafe office...

00:10:42.639 --> 00:10:44.200
There's a blue jacket of mine.

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:46.559
There's something inside it.

00:10:47.960 --> 00:10:48.799
Where?

00:10:48.919 --> 00:10:49.679
Can you give it to her?

00:10:50.720 --> 00:10:51.720
Her name is Luo Wenna.

00:10:52.679 --> 00:10:55.080
She's a sophomore at Yunhai High School.

00:10:56.519 --> 00:10:57.080
Chen Fan.

00:10:57.360 --> 00:10:57.960
I found out.

00:10:58.559 --> 00:11:00.639
I just called the teacher at Yunhai No. 1 High School.

00:11:00.879 --> 00:11:02.080
They said Wenjie's sister...

00:11:02.080 --> 00:11:03.639
Was picked up last night by a young man...

00:11:03.639 --> 00:11:04.799
...who claimed to be her brother.

00:11:05.159 --> 00:11:06.480
And she hasn't been back to school since.

00:11:07.240 --> 00:11:07.919
What?